<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="h-full">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
		<title>Login</title>
		{{ encore_entry_link_tags('app') }}
		{{ encore_entry_script_tags('app') }}
	</head>
	<body class="bg-gray-200 flex content-center justify-center items-center h-full">
		<div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center max-w-lg">
			<img src="/images/logo.svg" class="w-24 md:h-auto mb-8" alt="logo"/>
			<h1 class="text-2xl uppercase font-medium text-center max-w-md mb-8">Votre identifiant pour nous rejoindre</h1>
			<div>
				<form class="flex flex-col content-center justify-center items-center" method="post">
					<input type="text" id="inputEmail" name="email" placeholder="email" value="{{ last_username }}" class="border shadow-inner py-2 px-3 text-gray-700 w-80 focus:shadow-outline mb-3"/>
					<input type="password" name="password" id="inputPassword" placeholder="password" autocomplete="current-password" class="border shadow-inner py-2 px-3 text-gray-700 w-80 focus:shadow-outline">
					<div class="flex justify-between items-start options">
						<div class="remember flex w-8">
							<input type="radio" class="form-radio" name="accountType" value="personal">
							<span class="ml-2">Garder ma session ouverte</span>
						</div>
						<div class="forget">
							<a>Mot de passe oublié ?</a>
						</div>
					</div>
					<p>En vous connectant, vous acceptez de vous conformer à la Politique de confidentialité et aux Conditions générales de notre site.</p>
					<input type="hidden" name="_csrf_token" value="{{ csrf_token('authenticate') }}">
					<button class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" type="submit">Connexion</button>
					<p>Vous n'êtes pas encore membre ?
						<a>Rejoignez-nous.</a>
					</p>
				</form>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
